msgstr "獵人（只能擇一）：擅長偷襲"

#. [advancement]: id=hunter_2_2
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/units/quenoth/Youth.cfg:228
msgid "Hunter (choose only one): specialize in skirmishing"
msgstr "獵人（只能擇一）：擅長游擊"

